- [X] T007 [P] [Monitor-Test] Unit test: cost calculations match shared pricing config rates in `tests/unit/aiUsageMonitor.test.ts`
  - Test Anthropic formula: (inputTokens / 1_000_000) * 3 + (outputTokens / 1_000_000) * 15
    - Example: 30K input + 20K output = (30000/1M)*3 + (20000/1M)*15 = 0.09 + 0.30 = $0.39
  - Test OpenAI formula: (inputTokens / 1_000_000) * 5 + (outputTokens / 1_000_000) * 15
  - Test Google formula: (inputTokens / 1_000_000) * 0.25 + (outputTokens / 1_000_000) * 0.50
  - Test multi-provider aggregation sums correctly
  - Import COST_PER_1K_TOKENS from config/pricing.ts for test rates
