  - Verify trigger is 'file-watch'
- [ ] T009 [P] [Monitor-Test] Integration test: polling fallback works when file watcher disabled in `tests/integration/aiUsageUpdates.test.ts`
  - Disable file watcher, update data, verify event within 5s
  - Verify trigger is 'polling'
- [ ] T010 [P] [Monitor-Test] Integration test: dispose prevents memory leaks in `tests/integration/aiUsagePanel.test.ts`
