  - Verify AIUsageMonitor emits 'usage-update' within 500ms
  - Verify AIUsageProvider.refresh() called
  - Verify TreeView.getChildren() returns updated data
  - Assert: Full round-trip file write → panel update <1s
- [X] T010b [P] [Monitor-Test] Unit test: `forceRefresh()` clears cache and emits event in `tests/unit/aiUsageMonitor.test.ts`
  - Call getUsageData() to populate cache
