- `extension/src/council/UsageLogger.ts` - INTEGRATE only, call getUsageSummary()
- `extension/src/autonomous/MultiSessionBridgeWatcher.ts` - INTEGRATE only, read session data
- `extension/src/ui/ContextHealthStatusBar.ts` - REFERENCE only, pattern for status bar
- `extension/src/contextWindowProvider.ts` - REFERENCE only, pattern for TreeDataProvider
- All files in `extension/src/` not explicitly listed in tasks - Do not refactor

