## Notes

- **[P] tasks**: Different files, no dependencies - safe for parallel execution
- **[Story] labels**: Map tasks to user stories for traceability (US1-US4)
- **Test-first**: All test tasks (T006-T010, T018-T020, etc.) MUST be written BEFORE implementation
- **Verify tests fail**: Before implementing, run tests and confirm they fail (red in TDD cycle)
- **Independent stories**: Each US phase should be completable and testable independently
- **Commit frequency**: Commit after each task or logical group (e.g., all Phase 1 setup)
- **Checkpoints**: Stop at phase boundaries to validate independently before proceeding
- **File paths**: All paths are absolute from repository root (`extension/src/...`)
- **Code review**: Review tasks against plan.md and spec.md for coverage before starting

